## Шаг 5. Systemd units

### Кластер 1 (порт 9187) — на хосте 192.168.0.249

```bash
sudo tee /etc/systemd/system/postgres_exporter_cluster1.service > /dev/null <<'EOF'
[Unit]
Description=PostgreSQL Exporter - Cluster 1 (patroni-cluster)
Documentation=https://github.com/prometheus-community/postgres_exporter
After=network.target

[Service]
Type=simple
User=postgres_exporter
Group=postgres_exporter
EnvironmentFile=/etc/postgres_exporter/cluster1.env
ExecStart=/usr/local/bin/postgres_exporter \
    --extend.query-path=/etc/postgres_exporter/queries.yaml \
    --web.listen-address=:9187 \
    --web.telemetry-path=/metrics \
    --log.level=info \
    --collector.stat_bgwriter \
    --collector.stat_database \
    --collector.stat_user_tables \
    --collector.stat_statements \
    --collector.process_idle
Restart=on-failure
RestartSec=5s
NoNewPrivileges=yes

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
EOF
```

### Кластер 2 (порт 9187 если на другом хосте, 9188 если на том же)

```bash
sudo tee /etc/systemd/system/postgres_exporter_cluster2.service > /dev/null <<'EOF'
[Unit]
Description=PostgreSQL Exporter - Cluster 2
Documentation=https://github.com/prometheus-community/postgres_exporter
After=network.target

[Service]
Type=simple
User=postgres_exporter
